<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Budgetin - Aplikasi Pengelolaan Keuangan</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome untuk ikon -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        .hero-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff, #00c4b4);
            color: white;
            padding: 100px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 50px 50px;
        }
        .hero-section h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .hero-section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .btn-custom {
            background-color: #fff;
            color: #007bff;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-custom:hover {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #fff;
        }
        .feature-section {
            padding: 50px 0;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .feature-card i {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: #007bff;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">Budgetin</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/register">Register</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="hero-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Selamat Datang di Budgetin</h1>
            <p>Kelola keuangan Anda dengan mudah dan efisien. Pantau pemasukan, pengeluaran, dan saldo Anda dalam satu aplikasi.</p>
            <a href="/login" class="btn btn-custom">Mulai Sekarang</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <div class="feature-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-wallet"></i>
                        <h3>Manajemen Keuangan</h3>
                        <p>Catat pemasukan dan pengeluaran Anda dengan mudah.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i>
                        <h3>Laporan Keuangan</h3>
                        <p>Lihat ringkasan keuangan Anda dalam bentuk grafik.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <i class="fas fa-tags"></i>
                        <h3>Kategori Transaksi</h3>
                        <p>Atur transaksi Anda berdasarkan kategori.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>